      <p>
        In emergency situations like pandemics, floods, or natural disasters, the need for rapid response and efficient resource allocation is critical. Current systems often fail due to unpredictable demand, inaccessible areas, and delayed logistics. This project addresses the urgent need for intelligent models that ensure fast and resource-aware emergency relief.
